The Blackjack casino game application with c++
-----------------------------------------------

To run it from the terminal change your current directory to the this directory then: ./blackjack

To open the project in codeblocks just open codeblocks and choose open project.


Steps of execution :

Start the round
deal two Cards to each player
deal two cards to the house
flip the house's first card
display all players' cards and their total
display the house's hand (one card is hidden)
for all players
        while his hand's total didn't exceed 21
                offer players additional cards
flip the house's first card
display the house hand
while its hand's total didn't exceed 21
        offer additional cards to house
declare the winners
clear all hands 
End the round

